Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{It's your fault...}Tất cả là lỗi của cậu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{T-That's not true!}Không phải mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:21:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{That's why... you're going to see some pain!}Vậy nên... tôi sẽ cậu nếm mùi đau đớn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{W-Who is it?}A-Ai vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{Big Brother Yu?}Yuu-oniichan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{I'm gonna have to scare you a bit.}Anh sẽ dạy nhóc một bài học.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{W-What the–}C-Cái gì ?
